```python
# Instead of scanning files repeatedly
agent.scan_codebase()  # Slow, incomplete

# Use IntentGraph intelligence
analysis = load_intentgraph_report("analysis.json")
agent.understand_codebase(analysis)  # Fast, comprehensive
```

